      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="hr" style={display} />
    <div class="footer-holder" style={display}>
      <h4 class="slogan">WiiLink WFC is an open-source Nintendo Wi-Fi Connection
      replacement for your Wii!
	  <br><br>
